{
  "stem": "8753.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "May i take a drink of water?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] There were wire fences.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And many people used to sneak out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to-- the peasants also used to come to the wired fences and-- to sell some potatoes and bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were asking outrageous prices, so very few people had the money to-- to buy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, there were guards around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So if a guard came around to see the transactions, he would take away the-- the-- the food and beat up the-- the Jewish person.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the peasants used to run away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed in a large-- there was-- it was about a three story-- three-story building.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was facing the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And next door to that building was a brewer-- a brewery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, most houses in the ghetto were small houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a hospital in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, my sister got typhoid, and she wound-- she was in that hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lajcie.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's where she perished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, they burned the hospital with all the people in it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, I-- I painted a painting of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a very difficult painting to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in 1942, 1942.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I-- when our-- let me go back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- there was a panic in the ghetto that the liquidation would start.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my sister and myself ran away from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sarah and yourself?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sarah and myself ran away from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister wanted the whole family to run away, but again, my father was the type that he would be there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wanted to stay there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't want to move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I think I skipped a lot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have to get back.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
